                        <lb n="3" />societ&#224; apparivano a <persName>Marco Aurelio</persName> e a <persName>Lu&#61;
                        <lb break="no" n="4" />ciano</persName>&#44; ad <persName>Apollonio di <settlement>Tiana</settlement></persName>&#44; a <persName>Giuliano</persName>
                        <lb n="5" />come a <persName>Tertulliano</persName>&#44; ad <persName>Agostino</persName>&#44; ai <personGrp>martiri
                        <lb n="6" />del Circo</personGrp>&#46; <del rend="overstrike">Ero che</del> La mia mentalit&#224; &#232; come
